      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "G B BRAVE NZ (8) produced yet another strong performance last start when he battled on bravely to just miss out over 2190m at this track, adding to a string of recent minor placings. Gets a soft run on the inside of the second line but may need luck at some point. Won't find this any harder and he can take care of this line-up. LOSEASHOE (9) started from a wide draw on the second line last start. Pushed forward to settle handy then the effort told when 24 metres from the winner in tenth here over 2190m. May just need a bit of luck at some point from this difficult draw. Meets a similar quality field and is good enough to win a race of this calibre. ROCKNROLL LENNY (6) is in the mix following a fourth at his most recent appearance over 1790m at this venue. Top-three commodity. STARVIN MARVIN NZ (5) will be cherry-ripe after three runs back from a spell, the latest effort a fourth at this course two weeks ago. Ready to peak now.",
